-- Ukraine Picks Baker Tilly to Value Naftogaz for Pipeline Plan
-- B y   D a r y n a   K r a s n o l u t s k a
-- 2012-03-28T15:44:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-28/ukraine-picks-baker-tilly-to-value-naftogaz-for-pipeline-plan.html
Ukraine chose Baker Tilly
International to value state-owned NAK Naftogaz Ukrainy’s
natural gas pipelines and storage sites under a plan to manage
the assets with  Russia  and the European Union.  Baker Tilly’s Ukrainian unit won a tender for the work,
Naftogaz, based in the capital Kiev, said today in an e-mailed
statement. Ukraine will pay 4.1 million hryvnia ($510,000) for
the work, which should be completed by August, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Daryna Krasnolutska in Kiev at 
 dkrasnolutsk@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
